body:
Hey! So I felt like my last montage went really well, so here's a new one! This time I'm doing something different; instead of just showing the successful rushes, I'mm putting in the entire process of me trying to break a pretty heavily defended monument. If you enjoyed this video, please make sure to subscribe, and that will keep more videos coming :D

http://youtu.be/Ppe-qFtnAc4
